in landscape of products, projects, and community sentiments within first three months Appear in short videos explaining products and concepts and providing thought leadership to cryptocurrency users Assist in developing content for short video shoots, and uploading these videos Maintain company YouTube channels Regularly monitor and participate in social media conversations on Twitter, Reddit, Discord, Telegram, Slack, etc. promoting the company\u2019s projects and thought leadership in a highly positive light Develop one consistent identity across social media and video platforms and build a following and credibility Continuously inform founder, development and marketing leads of community sentiment regarding their projects and seek feedback to disseminate to community Identify community queries that need to be elevated for higher level responses The first several weeks of the role will be dedicated to developing expertise in the world of cryptocurrency and blockchain landscape Stay current on crypto projects and deeply research various technologies as they become relevant In addition to excellent written and verbal communication skills, the ideal candidate will also have: Strong on-camera proficiency and personality preferably demonstrated by existing Vimeo or YouTube-type channel Guru-level social media skills preferably demonstrated by a strong existing presence across numerous social media platforms Great sense of fun, humor and positivity that translates across video and social media communications General tech savvy/enthusiasm Strong interest in becoming an expert in cryptocurrency Video production/post-production experience a plus Demonstrated fluency with reading from a teleprompter without looking like you\u2019re reading from a teleprompter Foreign language fluency a plus Perks and Compensation We offer excellent training and professional development opportunities through various course materials and on-the-job training. Flexible work hours. Friendly, accepting workplace of people who like to roll up their sleeves and make things. Access to deep knowledge of all facets of cryptocurrency. Competitive salary. Profit sharing and equity in spun-off companies based on our technology portfolio. Paid Holidays, Vacation and Health insurance after 3 months. ORCA or Puget Sound Transit card for mass transit commuters. Equal Opportunity Employer. We actively seek to build a diverse workplace. Please send a resume and short introduction letter to beth@hornofthemoon.com. "
